                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- S4: BUILD — Code/Render Slider -->
    <section id="s4" class="light-sec">
        <div class="split-grid">
            <div style="padding-right: 4vw;">
                <div class="mono-label">PHASE 03 / BUILD</div>
                <h2>Hand-coded.<br>Every time.</h2>
                <p>We do not use page builders. They are bloated, slow, unmaintainable, and locked to specific platforms.</p>
                <p>Hand-coding gives you sub-1s load times, intentional placement of every DOM element, and zero hidden tracking scripts.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="interactive-panel float-y" data-speed="1.1" style="background: var(--c-white);">
                <div class="panel-header">
                    <span style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.7rem; color: rgba(2,6,13,0.5);">MARKUP</span>
                    <div class="interactive-badge">Interactive</div>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-hint" id="hint-slider">
                    <svg width="14" height="12" viewBox="0 0 14 12" fill="none"><path d="M1 6h12M4 3l-3 3 3 3M10 3l3 3-3 3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
                    Drag the slider to see how code becomes design
                </div>
                <div class="slider-container">
                    <span>RAW HTML</span>
                    <input type="range" min="0" max="2" value="0" id="codeSlider" oninput="onSliderInput()">
                    <span>INTERACTIVE</span>
                </div>
                <div class="split-view-container">
                    <div class="code-side" id="codeView">
&lt;button class="btn"&gt;<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;Book Call<br>
&lt;/button&gt;
                    </div>
                    <div class="render-side">
                        <button id="renderBtn" style="font-family: serif; background: #eee; border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 5px; color: black; border-radius:0; transition:none;">Book Call</button>
                    </div>
