                <p>On launch day, you get source code, hosting credentials, domain ownership, documentation, and a 30-minute training call. No ongoing dependency. You can end the engagement at any time and your site keeps running.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="interactive-panel float-y" data-speed="0.95" style="height: auto; min-height: 500px;">
                <div class="panel-header">
                    <div class="mono-label" style="border:none; padding:0; margin:0; color: var(--c-cyan); font-size: 0.65rem;">HANDOVER MANIFEST / SOLVUS TO CLIENT</div>
                    <div class="interactive-badge">Scroll to trigger</div>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-hint" id="hint-manifest">
                    <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none"><path d="M6 1v10M6 11l-3-3M6 11l3-3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                    Scroll down to trigger the handover sequence
                </div>
                <div class="panel-body" style="padding-top: 0;">
                    <ul class="manifest-list" id="manifestList">
                        <li><div class="checkbox"></div> Source code (Git repository, full history)</li>
                        <li><div class="checkbox"></div> Hosting account credentials</li>
                        <li><div class="checkbox"></div> Domain registrar access</li>
                        <li><div class="checkbox"></div> CMS / content admin access</li>
                        <li><div class="checkbox"></div> Google Business Profile ownership</li>
                        <li><div class="checkbox"></div> Analytics ownership transfer</li>
                        <li><div class="checkbox"></div> Documentation (maintenance guidelines)</li>
                        <li><div class="checkbox"></div> 30-min training session recording</li>
                        <li><div class="checkbox"></div> 30-day support window activated</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div id="manifestComplete" style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--c-cyan); text-align: right; margin-top: 2rem; opacity: 0; transform: translateY(0); transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1); letter-spacing: 0.15em;">HANDOVER COMPLETE</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- S6: ENGINEERING SPEC -->
    <section id="s6" class="light-sec" style="padding-top: 6vw;">
        <div style="text-align: center; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
            <div class="mono-label">SPECIFICATION / ENGINEERING</div>
            <h2>Under the hood.</h2>
            <p style="margin: 0 auto;">Details nobody else bothers to mention. These apply to every Solvus build.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="eng-grid">
            <div class="eng-card"><div class="mono-label">LIGHTHOUSE TARGET</div><p style="margin:0; font-size: 1rem;">Minimum 95/100 on mobile. Measured on every push.</p></div>
            <div class="eng-card"><div class="mono-label">LCP BUDGET</div><p style="margin:0; font-size: 1rem;">Under 1.5s on 4G. Under 2.5s on slow 3G.</p></div>
            <div class="eng-card"><div class="mono-label">CLS BUDGET</div><p style="margin:0; font-size: 1rem;">Under 0.05. Below Google's good threshold.</p></div>
            <div class="eng-card"><div class="mono-label">WCAG LEVEL</div><p style="margin:0; font-size: 1rem;">AA minimum, AAA on text contrast for legibility.</p></div>
            <div class="eng-card"><div class="mono-label">SEMANTIC HTML</div><p style="margin:0; font-size: 1rem;">Used correctly. Nav, main, article, real headings in order.</p></div>
            <div class="eng-card"><div class="mono-label">SCHEMA MARKUP</div><p style="margin:0; font-size: 1rem;">LocalBusiness and RealEstateAgent injected as JSON-LD.</p></div>
            <div class="eng-card"><div class="mono-label">IMAGE STRATEGY</div><p style="margin:0; font-size: 1rem;">Modern formats (WebP/AVIF), responsive srcset, lazy-loaded.</p></div>
            <div class="eng-card"><div class="mono-label">PROGRESSIVE ENHANCEMENT</div><p style="margin:0; font-size: 1rem;">Site works without JS for core content.</p></div>
        </div>
